{"title":"西财摄记 | Treat or trick","uid":"01585c548678d4e5aca9b3e8f16585d8","slug":"推文12","date":"2021-10-30T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T16:03:09.042Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文12.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000053925.png","content":"<p>“你既是我的生路，亦是我的死途”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000046610.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000046610\"></p>\n<p>我曾任爱意在我心底肆意生长</p>\n<p>随红玫瑰枯萎</p>\n<p>连同我的身体一起腐烂</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000053925.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000053925\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000057541.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000057541\"></p>\n<p>在万圣节夜晚</p>\n<p>我混入扮鬼的人群</p>\n<p>明目张胆找寻你的眼睛</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000104453.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000104453\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000108720.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000108720\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000112416.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000112416\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000119237.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000119237\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000122652.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000122652\"></p>\n<p>希望你快乐</p>\n<p>希望你快乐</p>\n<p>希望你 离开我</p>\n<p>无法快乐</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000131894.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000131894\"></p>\n<p>爱人 你太知道 </p>\n<p> 害一个人怎样害一生</p>\n<p>在她干净无菌主题乐园加进了坏人</p>\n<p>可怜那颗心 不知不觉 </p>\n<p>变得狠</p>\n<p>狠得好坏不分</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000140116.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000140116\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000147459.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000147459\"></p>\n<p>身体里 有个什么 已被刺破</p>\n<p>爱情的神经 以后 一快乐 就难过</p>\n<p>——《天真有邪》</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000154033.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000154033\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000158161.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000158161\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000201624.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000201624\"></p>\n<p>遗憾太重的人啊 逝后会成灰孤魂</p>\n<p>或许就在万圣之夜</p>\n<p>游荡人间</p>\n<p>“treat or trick”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000213076.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000213076\"></p>\n<p>祝愿这里的你</p>\n<p>携你所爱 </p>\n<p>在这人间 不留遗憾</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>感谢</summary>\n<p><p>摄 | 钟志涛 赵思宇</p>\n<p>模特 | 张迈</p>\n<p>文 | 张迈 赵思宇</p>\n<p>排版 | 赵思宇</p>\n</p>\n</details>\n","text":"“你既是我的生路，亦是我的死途” 我曾任爱意在我心底肆意生长 随红玫瑰枯萎 连同我的身体一起腐烂 在万圣节夜晚 我混入扮鬼的人群 明目张胆找寻你的眼睛 希望你快乐 希望你快乐 希望你 离开我 无法快乐 爱人 你太知道 害一个人怎样害一生 在她干净无菌主题乐园加进了坏人 可怜那颗心...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":331,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":8,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"冬","slug":"冬","count":2,"path":"api/tags/冬.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303234741533.png"},"mail":{"icon":"/img/mail.png","link":"mailto:271215314@qq.com"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"秋日特辑 | 去川西，去最接近天堂的地方","uid":"74544a5b5216c424c5b8f8e62fd899f7","slug":"推文13","date":"2021-11-07